N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 160.32 - Education credit

State Regulations

Application for full educational credit may be made by
individuals who have completed an approved course of study in another
jurisdiction that equals or exceeds the number of hours and content required
for New York State licensure. Notes
